## gpp-decrypt

When you see SMB on a Windows box
- run smb* scripts with NMAP to check for possible easy wins
- smbclient is used to interact with shares
- "smbclient -L" to list shares
- "smbmap -H -R" to list recursively (with access info)
- If connected, turn recurse ON and prompt OFF, then mget * to download all files locally

